1. Serialization and Deserialization
--Serialization of json is conversion of one json object into .NET object
--Deserialization is converting the .NET object into a json object

Gson is by google and widely used for serialization and deserialization of Json

JSON object
{
"key" : "value"
"key" : "value"
}

JSON element
"key" : "value"

JSON Array
"key":[{
        "key" : "value",
        "key" : "value",
        "key" : "value"
        },
        {
        "key" : "value",
        "key" : "value",
        "key" : "value"
        },
        {"key" : "value",
         "key" : "value",
         "key" : "value"
         }]

Whenever we access value of a key, it returns JSON element
